title.narrative: Increasing the overall average and subject's examination averages from 2010/2011 baseline

comment.narrative: Source: 2010/2011 Bac results.Note: (i) Baseline changed from 2006 to 2011, per Board approval under the Additional Financing.(ii) Weighted average utilized. (iii) Indicator not comparable to previous years/ISRs due to methodological changes.

target.value: Increasing the overall average and subject’s examinations averages from the baseline of 2010/2011

comment.narrative: The end of project target was changed to the above with the AF due to an overhaul in the administration of the Baca exams inMoldova.
Source: 2012/2013 Bac results.Note: Data not comparable to 2010/2011 or 2011/2012 data due to a change in application procedure.

title.narrative: The difference in achievement between secondary school students in rural and urban schools, on average, is decreased.

comment.narrative: Source: 2010/2011 Bac results.Note: (i) Indicator not comparable to previous years/ISRs due to methodological changes. (ii)Datashows rural students outperforming urban ones, which raises serious red flags on the reliability of the results.

target.value: Reducing the gap in average exam results for rural and urban students by at least 6% vs. baseline.

comment.narrative: Source: 2012/2013 Bac results.Note: While the overall average shows gap is closing, data not comparable to 2010/2011 or2011/2012 data due to a change in application procedure.
